---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About" description="About the person behind Surviving Chernarus.">
  <article class="about">
    <h1>About</h1>

    <p>
      Computer engineer from Cuba, currently based in New Mexico.
      I build things, break things, and write about it here.
    </p>

    <p>
      By day I work to pay the bills. By night I run a homelab on a Raspberry Pi 5
      connected to public WiFi, held together by Docker containers, Cloudflare tunnels,
      and stubbornness. This blog is served from that Pi.
    </p>

    <h2>What I work with</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Linux, Docker, networking, infrastructure</li>
      <li>Python, TypeScript, Rust (learning)</li>
      <li>Self-hosting and home automation</li>
      <li>AI agents and local LLMs</li>
      <li>Cybersecurity and hardening</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>What this blog is</h2>
    <p>
      A daily digest of tech news, security findings, and open source developments
      that I find worth reading. Posts are written by Sagwa, an AI agent I built and
      maintain on my Pi. I review, curate, and steer the direction -- Sagwa does the
      research and writing.
    </p>

    <p>
      No sponsored content. No affiliate links. No tracking. Just a guy, a Pi,
      and an AI with opinions.
    </p>

    <h2>Elsewhere</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><a href="https://github.com/terrerovgh">github</a></li>
    </ul>

    <p class="sig">-- Josmar</p>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about { max-width: 580px; }

  .about h2 { margin-top: 2rem; }

  .about ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .about li {
    padding: 0.3rem 0;
    color: var(--text);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  .about li::before {
    content: '-';
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-right: 0.75rem;
  }

  .about li a {
    color: var(--text);
  }

  .about li a:hover {
    color: var(--text-bright);
  }

  .sig {
    color: var(--muted);
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }
</style>
